Laxmii was taken in by a kind Muslim named Abdul Chacha, who had a mentally disabled son. They formed a close relationship.
Laxmii adopted another transgender girl named Geeta and worked hard to support her financially.
Laxmii had conflicts with MLA Girja illegally seizing her property.
After hearing her story, Asif willingly let her possess him once more to complete her revenge.
Laxmii killed Girja's wife and bodyguards but could not enter the Goddess Durga temple, being a ghost.
After hearing Laxmii's story, Asif forcibly dragged Girja out of the Goddess Durga temple.
